stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle : snapshot idle

    Idle --> Connecting : start run
    Connecting --> Running : manifest ready and session opened
    Connecting --> Failed : pre-launch failure

    Running --> Completed : eof
    Running --> Stopped : explicit stop
    Running --> Failed : runtime exception

    Completed --> Idle : next start replaces snapshot
    Stopped --> Idle : next start replaces snapshot
    Failed --> Idle : next start replaces snapshot

    note right of Connecting
      PipelineSessionService.start(...)
      plan: RunPlan
      sequence_manifest: SequenceManifest?
    end note

    note right of Running
      StreamingSlamBackend.start_session(...)
      latest_packet: FramePacket
      latest_slam_update: SlamUpdate
      num_sparse_points / num_dense_points
    end note

    note right of Completed
      SlamSession.close() -> SlamArtifacts
      slam: SlamArtifacts
      summary: RunSummary
      stage_manifests: StageManifest[]
    end note
